<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٤١٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">غُنْدَرٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6245">مُعَاوِيَةَ بْنِ قُرَّةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">«اللَّهُمَّ لَا عَيْشَ إِلَّا عَيْشُ الْآخِرَهْ … فَأَصْلِحِ الْأَنْصَارَ وَالْمُهَاجِرَهْ.»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>